  "records": {
    "description": "Filters and then uses crafter to compact items (eg such as iron ingots) with 8/9 items to 1 crafting recipes.",
    "features": [
      "Low Threshold SSI Filter: It uses SSI filter with minimal Threshold and Prefill.",
      "Precise Crafting: These crafters only start crafting when they detect a completely full SS9 crafter.",
      "Global SS11 Line with Recovery Function: The system uses a global SS11 line to control the crafters. It can empty an overflowing crafter that has stopped by pulsing an SS15 signal.",
      "Includes box loader variants for 8x, 16x, and 24x."
    ],
    "considerations": [
      "For box loader variants, there is a small chance (~1 in 50 million boxes) of losing a box"
    ],
    "instructions": [
      "Setup filters according to ACG001",
      "Input items using a waterstream"
    ],
    "compatibility": "1.21+"
  },
